## Netlify security headers — applies to every route
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; img-src 'self' data:; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src https://fonts.gstatic.com; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; form-action https://app.kit.com; frame-src https://app.kit.com; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'

## Long-cache fingerprintable static assets
/images/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
